# Privacy Policy for TMHCI Mobile App

*Last Updated: [7th December 2023]*

Welcome to the mobile application ("App") provided by TMHCI ("we," "us," or "our"). This Privacy Policy is designed to inform you about the types of information we may collect from you or that you may provide when you download, install, register with, access, or use the TMHCI mobile app (collectively, the "Services"). This Privacy Policy also explains how we use, disclose, and protect that information.

Please read this Privacy Policy carefully before using the App. By using the App, you agree to the terms and conditions of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with the terms and conditions of this Privacy Policy, please do not use the App.

## 1. Information We Collect

### 1.1. Information You Provide to Us
We may collect information that you provide directly to us, such as when you register for an account, use certain features of the App, or contact us for customer support.

### 1.2. Automatically Collected Information
When you use the App, we may automatically collect certain information, including but not limited to your device type, device ID, IP address, and usage information.

### 1.3. Location Information
The App may collect real-time information about the location of your device for providing location-based services. You can control the collection of location information through your device settings.

### 1.4. Information from Third Parties
We may receive information about you from third parties, such as social media platforms or other third-party partners.

## 2. How We Use Your Information

We may use the information we collect for various purposes, including:

- Providing and improving the App.
- Customizing your experience.
- Responding to your requests and providing customer support.
- Sending you updates, newsletters, and promotional messages.
- Analyzing and monitoring usage patterns.

## 3. Disclosure of Your Information

We may share your information with third parties under the following circumstances:

- With your consent.
- To comply with legal obligations.
- To protect and defend our rights and property.
- In connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of all or a portion of our assets.

## 4. Your Choices

You can manage your account settings and preferences within the App. You can opt-out of receiving promotional communications by following the instructions provided in the messages.

## 5. Security

We take reasonable measures to protect the information we collect from unauthorized access or disclosure.

## 6. Children's Privacy

The App is not intended for individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have collected personal information from a child under 13, please contact us.

## 7. Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The most current version will be posted on the App, and your continued use constitutes acceptance of the updated Privacy Policy.

## 8. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [spark23africa@gmail.com].

By using the App, you agree to the terms and conditions of this Privacy Policy.
